## Import



Using `pulumi import`, import WAF Regional Byte Match Set using the id. For example:

```sh
 $ pulumi import aws:wafregional/byteMatchSet:ByteMatchSet byte_set a1b2c3d4-d5f6-7777-8888-9999aaaabbbbcccc
```
